-- MOVES-AKG appoints Ward head of communications
-- 
-- Fri Jul 25, 2014 04:14AM EDT
-- None



July 25 (Reuters) - AKG Actuaries & Consultants, a provider of information, ratings and consultancy to the financial services industry, appointed Matt Ward as its head of communications.

AKG said Ward will take the lead on marketing and communication activities at AKG and support the continued expansion of the company's core provider profile services and the development of its consultancy business.